	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Regarde,<delay8 /> <tag a="110" b="3" />!<delay20 />
Tu me refiles un truc,<delay8 /> et moi,<delay8 /> je m'en
