<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Observe bien <tag a="50" b="1" /><tag a="125" b="5" arg="0xcd00" /> que je porte<tag a="110" b="0" /> <anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ça y est,<delay8 /> ça te revient?</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Alors,<delay8 /> comment est-ce que <anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="1" /><tag a="125" b="5" arg="0xcd00" /> que tu m'as refilé<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x17 0xcd00 0x0 0x2 0x65 0x0" /> me va?<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />J'avoue que je suis plutôt satisfait
