	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Ça me coûte de l'admettre,<delay8 /> <anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />mais <tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /> a parfois bon goût en matière d'habits.<pageBreak /><gender1 m="Il" f="Elle" /> m'a donné cet<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x17 0xcd00 0x0 0x4 0x74 0x65 0x0" /> élégant<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x17 0xcd00 0x0 0x2 0x65 0x0" /> <tag a="125" b="5" arg="0xcd00" />.<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Qu'est-ce que t'en dis,<delay8 /> <tag a="110" b="5" />?</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Alors,<delay8 /> comment me va <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x18 0xcd00 0x10 0x63 0x65 0x20 0x70 0x65 0x74 0x69 0x74 0x18 0x63 0x65 0x74 0x74 0x65 0x20 0x70 0x65 0x74 0x69 0x74 0x65 0x0" /> <tag a="125" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />?<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Je ne risque pas d'oublier que c'est
toi qui me l'as donné<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x18 0xcd00 0x0 0x2 0x65 0x0" />, <tag a="110" b="6" />!</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Bon,<delay8 /> <anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />je porte <tag a="50" b="1" /><tag a="125" b="6" arg="0xcd00" /> que tu m'as donné<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x18 0xcd00 0x0 0x2 0x65 0x0" />,<delay8 /> et honnêtement<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Je crois que je vais <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x18 0xcd00 0x4 0x6c 0x65 0x4 0x6c 0x61 0x0" /> garder,<delay8 /> <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Alors, qu'en dis-tu?<delay8 /> Je crois que
je pourrais m'habituer à porter
<tag a="50" b="2" /><tag a="125" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />.
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Merci de me l'avoir donné<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x18 0xcd00 0x0 0x2 0x65 0x0" />, <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Regarde bien mon look, <delay8 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />tu vois un
