	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd01" /> m'a donné <tag a="50" b="2" /><tag a="125" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />.<delay8 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Vu qu'<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x10e 0xcd00 0x4 0x69 0x6c 0x8 0x65 0x6c 0x6c 0x65 0x0" /> s'habille avec un minimum
